OL,3,CCalls for changes to Guernsey's
OL,4,Cplanning policy to help social housing
OL,5,Ccrisis
OL,7,FA deputy has admitted that only one
OL,8,Fnew unit of social housing will be
OL,9,Fcomplete on the island this year.
OL,11,FIt comes as 348 households are on
OL,12,Fwaiting lists.
OL,14,FNo new social housing was built last
OL,15,Fyear on Guernsey.
OL,17,FThe President of Guernsey's Social
OL,18,FSecurity & Employment Committee,
OL,19,FDeputy Peter Roffey said: "It's
OL,20,Fnowhere near good enough."
