OL,7,FBrodie Williams, who is 19-years-old,
OL,8,Fis currently on the waiting list for a
OL,9,Fsocial house.
OL,11,FShe said: 'I lost my mum when I was 14
OL,12,Fso I moved in with my sister for a few
OL,13,Fmonths but there wasn't really room.
OL,15,F"I moved to my mum's friends but the
OL,16,Flandlord put the rent up and then I
OL,17,Fhad nowhere to go, so me and my sister
OL,18,Fcame to Action for Children".
